                    Tax Time Helpers
   [clearpixel.gif]

   Philadelphia Business Tax... Electronic Filing

   Business Privilege, Net Profits, School Income, Wage Reconciliation Tax
   Returns can be filed electronically by using the City´s "ROAD" program.
   Business and Wage Tax Payments can be made electronically by using ACH
   Debits or ACH Credits. Both programs are sponsored by the Philadelphia
   Department of Revenue.
   [clearpixel.gif]

   Philadelphia´s Plain Talk Tax Guide

   From the Philadelphia Department of Revenue, this  tax guide provides a
   brief description of the City of Philadelphia's taxes and water/sewer
   charges. This handy reference offers a helpful overview of what your
   obligations might be. Taxes that apply to both individuals and to
   businesses are included.
   [clearpixel.gif]

